Params: {1: '1', 2: 'Tired Corrupted', 3: '(Its arm jams as it raises its weapon) ...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Relax, I can still take on another dozen of you. So come at me, bro! Show me what you got! No one goes easy on me!', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Tired Corrupted', 3: '(Its power supply warning goes off while its frame lets out black smoke) ...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "Although Roland got away, he couldn't have gone far in that state...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Not to mention he'd sent all the Corrupted he got trying to stop me...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Save me the trouble of hunting you all down one by one later! Let's put all you eggs into one basket, and let's get cracking!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Elite Corrupted', 3: '(Wipes the gold dust from its blade barehanded) ...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "That's more like it! Don't keep sending me minions!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: "(Shrugs off the arm from a fallen Corrupted) No wonder I'm sensing less gold dust in the air...", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "The minions were in charge of absorbing the glitter, weren't they? You're using them as a filter!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Kamui', 3: "Oh, your kind doesn't really give a crap who lives or dies, do you?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Kamui', 3: 'Yeah, yeah, I know. Here I come to kick your ass!', 4: '1'}
